## Link status
## Reply: up (or down)
:/# cat /sys/class/net/eth0/operstate
up

## Link speed
:/# cat /sys/class/net/eth1/speed 
1000

:/# ip link show enp2s0
2: enp2s0: <BROADCAST,MULTICAST,UP,LOWER_UP> mtu 1500 qdisc mq state UP mode DEFAULT group default qlen 1000
    link/ether 00:a0:c9:00:00:0f brd ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff

